<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.1">
<l>arava ṇaiyā yāya rēṟē yamma muṇṇat tuyile ḻāyē</l>
<l>yiravu muṇṇā tuṟaṅki nīpō yiṉṟu mucci koṇṭa tālō</l>
<l>vuravuṅ kāṇēṉ vayiṟa caintāy vaṉamu laikaḷ cōrntu pāyat</l>
<l>tiruvu ṭaiya vāyma ṭuttut tiḷaittu taittup paruki ṭāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with a serpent for a bed! Bull among cowherds!</l>
<l>Rise from sleep to drink [my] breast milk.</l>
<l>You went to sleep without eating [last] night,</l>
<l>and today it is nearing noon, is it not?</l>
<l>I do not see [you] in motion, you with the rumbling belly,</l>
<l>as [my milk] trickles, spreading [from my] beautiful breasts,</l>
<l>[come and] drink, playing and kicking,</l>
<l>suckle with [your] holy mouth!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
